---
import { CONTACT } from "../lib/site";
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-20 pt-16 sm:pb-28 sm:pt-24">
  <p
    class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-signal"
  >
    <span aria-hidden="true">&#9679;</span>
    {CONTACT.availability} &middot; {CONTACT.location} &middot; {CONTACT.workPreference}
  </p>

  <h1
    class="mt-6 max-w-3xl font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.1] text-paper sm:text-6xl"
  >
    Full-stack engineer. I ship web and mobile apps end to end, from data
    model to production.
  </h1>

  <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted sm:text-xl">
    Three years building multi-tenant SaaS, payments infrastructure, and
    mobile apps end to end. Most of that work is commercial and stays
    private. Below are a few things I'm building in the open instead.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
    <a
      href="#projects"
      class="rounded bg-signal px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm text-ink transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
    >
      View projects
    </a>
    <a
      href="#contact"
      class="rounded border border-panel-line px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm text-paper transition-colors hover:border-trace"
    >
      Get in touch
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
